Description:
CONTEMPORARY STYLE, VICTORIAN INSPIRED
Perfectly positioned, this balconied terrace makes a sound investment or ideal low-maintenance lifestyle opportunity in one of inner-Melbourne's most vibrant pockets. Beyond its period-style facade complete with lacework and tessellated tiles, the home's immaculate interior highlights two double bedrooms (with robes), main bathroom and powder room (second WC), open lounge and dining areas complemented by a central kitchen. Add to this gas heating and split-system air conditioning, separate laundry, plus a private undercover courtyard complete with secure carport via rollerdoor (remote-controlled) to Palmer Lane. Easy access to Victoria Park Station, Johnston Street buses, Smith Street trams, cafes and restaurants - city living at its best! Nelson Alexander Pty Ltd

Description:
Absolute Blue Chip Terrace Living...
Sale by set date 29th April 2015 at 1pm. In a quiet tree-lined street walking distance to cafes & transport, this extended Victorian terrace is set to impress with its free-flowing design and top-quality features throughout. Filled with natural light, the home's impeccable interior boasts two double bedrooms (with robes) and contemporary-style bathroom, superb kitchen/dining, spacious rear living area opening out to a delightfully private entertainers' courtyard. Other highlights of the home include split-system heating/cooling, high ornate ceilings, attic storage, European laundry, quality carpets and polished timber floors. Executive inner-city living at its best, walking distance to Johnston Street shops and cafes, trams and trains to the CBD.

Description:
Sunsets, city views and extraordinary space
Unique in every way imaginable, this amazing two-level townhouse styled apartment redefines the concept of inner-city living with its expansive floor plan (176sqm), designer features and breathtaking city panorama. Completely detached from the bustle of Hoddle Street, the home's spacious and serene interior boasts three bedrooms (extra-large master with WIR and ensuite), stylish main bathroom and additional powder room (third WC), gourmet stone-top kitchen with soft-close drawers and European appliances, vast open-plan living and dining areas with high vaulted ceilings opening out to a large entertainers' terrace complete with motorized awning and spectacular city views. Other highlights include split-system heating and cooling, second balcony, plus secure entry foyer, lift, two lower-level car spaces and large storage cage with easy access via Islington Street. On the fringe of East Melbourne and Richmond, it's walking distance to Victoria Parade trams, Victoria Street restaurants, North Richmond Station and Fitzroy Gardens. Absolutely one of a kind!

Description:
Synergy Of Style, Sophistication & Space
A progression of space from historic Victorian Distillery to creative collaboration of living, work and art, this compelling two-level apartment is designed with aesthetic vision to inspire, delight and adapt ad infinitum. At once a contemporary home, a studio, an office and a lifestyle; a cleverly conceived interior capturing natural light and your imagination merges state-of-the-art style, refined craftsmanship and absolute attention to detail in a sought-after East Melbourne-fringe location. This tightly-held modern residence's flexible floorplan includes main bedroom with city views and smart ensuite, two separate studio spaces, lounge area with excellent entertainment unit, vast living or office zone including kitchenette/bar, integrated designer kitchen with top-line German appliances, powder room, heating/cooling, extensive storage, east-face balcony, roof space on title and secure basement parking. Current vendors have been living and working from this space for 15 years.

Description:
Location, luxury and grand proportions
A warehouse conversion like no other with its towering 5m ceilings and vast two-level floorplan, this spectacular apartment delivers the ultimate in city-edge style, space and flexibility (approx 200sqm). A captivating mix of industrial heritage and modern elegance, the home's versatile design highlights an enormous upstairs bedroom with robes, deluxe ensuite complete with spa bath, adjoining nursery, expansive study area and retreat/lounge (potential bedroom) with Juliette balcony. Downstairs: extraordinarily spacious open-plan living and dining areas complemented by a new stone-top kitchen with Miele/Blanco appliances, designer bathroom and impressive storage spaces throughout. Hydronic heating and Daikin split-system a/c add to the appeal, plus a private outdoor entertaining deck, intercom/secure entry and two undercover car spaces, as well as residents' rooftop terrace to complete this unique package. Stroll to Smith Street cafes and restaurants, Victoria Parade trams and Fitzroy Gardens.

Description:
Massive One Bedroom! Price to Sell!
This spacious apartment in the Islington building, Collingwood Street gives you modern styling, and the best of locations, perfect for the savvy investor or occupiers looking for space an light.
The generous bedroom invites bright easterly light, the property is fresh, clean, and will appeal to investors and occupiers alike. The spacious living and dining gives you a retreat from the hustle and bustle, with plenty of space for a study and entertaining accented beautifully by 3 large windows allowing for great airflow and lots of light. The kitchen is fully appointed with 4 gas burner, fan forced oven and extractor fan, with heaps of storage for your culinary dreams. Generous bedroom with built in robe, spacious bathroom and Air conditioning, what more could you ask for?
Perfectly located near public transport and the major arterial, this property gives you the choice of leaving the car at home, or hitting the road without any fuss. When you are only ten minutes from the CBD by bike or tram, the carspace is going to come in handy.

Description:
Top floor Penthouse - Approx 105sqm
Under Offer - A dynamic location in the heart of cosmopolitan Collingwood, this top-floor Marque apartment delivers a modern oasis of quality and style - complete with spectacular northerly views. A prime corner position offering an abundance of natural light, the apartment's stylish interior comprises two double bedrooms (both with robes) and deluxe bathroom, stone-top kitchen with stainless steel appliances, spacious open-plan living/dining area with double doors leading out to a big north-facing entertainers' terrace with a brilliant 180° urban vista. Other features include timber floors throughout, high ceilings, split-system cooling/heating, European laundry, intercom, plus lift access, secure entry foyer, two lower-level car spaces and storage cage. Executive lifestyle or blue-chip investment, its perfect either way with easy access to trams, shops, cafes and everything else this vibrant inner-Melbourne precinct has to enjoy.
Agent - Hockingstuart
Charles Atkins : 0405 287 112

HERITAGE CHARACTER WITH CONTEMPORARY STYLE
On the ground floor of the acclaimed 'Bohemia' complex, part of the heritage Foy and Gibson warehouse precinct, this elegant one bedroom apartment offers the best of inner-city conversion style, moments from Smith Street's newest restaurants and Gertrude Street galleries. With the advantage of a second frontage and security court entrance from Little Oxford Street, this high- ceilinged residence with rustic brick walls and industrial detail offers a spacious living and dining room open to a kitchen complete with Smeg appliances and custom cabinetry, large double bedroom with opaque glass feature wall, and an ultra-stylish bathroom/concealed laundry. Included are secure basement parking, video security entry, polished bamboo floors, bespoke BIRs, air conditioning and ceiling fans.

Description:
COOL AND CLASSY IN COLLINGWOOD!
This stylish apartment in the striking wave contour development just around the corner from Smith St cafes and Gertrude St boutiques is a must-see for home buyers and smart investors. Set over two levels just up from the secure street entry, are two double bedrooms (BIRs), an expansive living and dining room open to a neat kitchen and flowing to a wide balcony overlooking plane trees, and a smart bathroom/concealed laundry. Including two secure car spaces, this classic CBD retreat features new carpets, parquetry floors and split-system air conditioning.
